snippet.title: Babylon 5: I've Found Her "Danger And Opportunity" Intro
snippet.description:
The Intro sequence to the PC/MAC game of Babylon 5: I've Found Her "Danger And Opportunity".

Sorry, no XFire counterpart link for this game video as XFire has once again borked their video uploads.

The game is free and can be found/downloaded from:
http://ifhgame.ru/main/
